title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 72: Featuring Devan Dubnyk
description:
On this week's show, Minnesota Wild goalie Devan Dubnyk calls in to talk about his early career adversity, the mystery that is goaltender interference (along with a suggestion), being a big Barstool guy, and much more. Additionally, Whits and RA discuss the current playoff races, whether people are sleeping on the Caps, the hot Blues, potential playoff goalie controversies, being a degen (and having an 0-13-1 week), college signings, and a bunch of other stuff our scatterbrains get to.Â 


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
